      "comment_id" : 94134021,
      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
      "body" : "Your working directory can be found via the pwdx &lt;PID&gt; command. First do a ps -ef| grep java, find your PID for your java app, then run pwdx &lt;PID&gt;. It&#39;ll tell you the working directory."
